{"tid":429374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙士年49萬買西環納米盤　業主狂賺近9倍離場","createTime":"2017-10-08T23:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T09:31:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f87864e8339c22b603c2b5d47c323b81faaae069","tid":429374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:48:02.000Z","msg":"利嘉閣地產皇牌屋苑西南中環分行(A組)助理分區經理鄭敬曦表示，新近促成堅尼地城嘉輝花園C座高層6室成交，單位實用面積約236方呎，建築面積約289方呎，單位為兩房兩廳間隔，外望享開揚景觀，獲買家以483萬港元承接，折合實用面積呎價約20,466元，建築面積呎價約16,713元。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2003年5月以約49萬元買入，持貨14年，至今轉售，帳面獲利約434萬元，升幅逾8.8倍。 <br />\n<br />\n嘉輝花園現時約有18個放盤單位，入場費470萬元。 <br />\n－－－－－－ <br />\n《骰寶坊》誠邀各地【賭王】【賭后】挑戰神人境界，每日更有百萬籌碼等你領取！ <br />\n立即免費下載，體驗《骰寶坊》最真實、刺激的多人在線骰寶遊戲！ <br />\n遊戲下載：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/7JP2hm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7JP2hm&d=pJlKXLkXiGzccCl%2Fn%2FAQ6wHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=b5e8d483\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7JP2hm</a>"},{"pid":"289328eff993a2aa502bbf998f255d7d090dff63","tid":429374,"uid":21120,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:50:25.000Z","msg":"236呎間到兩房兩廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無則睇"},{"pid":"519360b6333e3e080eeadeca01486608aa5c93a7","tid":429374,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T23:52:34.000Z","msg":"個廳有無一百呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4943b310fe8a3dcb62d0f8d4062f9cf44e76a0","tid":429374,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:01:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20171008/mobile/bkn-20171008112711298-1008_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20171008%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20171008112711298-1008_00842_001.